564
00:40:54,852 --> 00:40:56,754
I SAW FRANKEN SPREADING
SOMETHING LIKE POWDER

565
00:40:56,821 --> 00:40:59,590
DON'T TELL ME THAT IT'S POISON

566
00:41:01,192 --> 00:41:03,694
MINORU TOKACHI WAS ABOUT
TO BE KILLED BY A MONSTER?

567
00:41:30,621 --> 00:41:33,924
ANTI-BACTERIAL SPRAY

568
00:42:03,587 --> 00:42:05,022
What are you doing?

569
00:42:06,690 --> 00:42:07,791
Ken.

570
00:42:09,994 --> 00:42:11,495
Seiya.

571
00:42:14,331 --> 00:42:18,202
I may be able to kill the bacteria
that live in my body if I drink this.

572
00:42:20,137 --> 00:42:22,640
Wait a minute. I don't think so.

573
00:42:23,707 --> 00:42:24,542
Let me try.

574
00:42:24,608 --> 00:42:26,944
Wait! Wait a minute.

575
00:42:30,180 --> 00:42:31,248
What are you doing?

576
00:42:34,351 --> 00:42:35,686
Tsugumi.

577
00:42:41,125 --> 00:42:42,560
Seiya.

578
00:42:45,529 --> 00:42:47,965
I am sorry for what I have done.

579
00:42:48,599 --> 00:42:50,501
You helped me a lot.

580
00:42:51,068 --> 00:42:52,836
You taught me a lot of things.

581
00:42:54,705 --> 00:42:56,073
I'm sorry.

582
00:43:00,077 --> 00:43:03,781
I will kill the bacteria so that
I can live in the human world.

583
00:43:03,847 --> 00:43:05,816
Wait! It's not like that.

584
00:43:05,883 --> 00:43:07,318
Don't take it wrong.

585
00:43:07,918 --> 00:43:09,219
Don't take it wrong.

586
00:43:11,221 --> 00:43:13,257
I put you on the radio.

587
00:43:14,892 --> 00:43:16,694
I encouraged you

588
00:43:18,028 --> 00:43:19,029
to go on the radio.

589
00:43:20,931 --> 00:43:24,068
I wanted to keep you away from Tsugumi.

590
00:43:25,936 --> 00:43:27,504
I thought Tsugumi would come to her senses

591
00:43:27,571 --> 00:43:29,640
if you caused trouble on the radio.

592
00:43:30,207 --> 00:43:31,542
So she wouldn't love you.

593
00:43:32,209 --> 00:43:33,978
She wouldn't fall in love with you.

594
00:43:36,246 --> 00:43:38,248
So, I met Amakusa.

595
00:43:40,017 --> 00:43:41,852
I told him that you are a monster.

596
00:43:43,520 --> 00:43:48,692
I wished that you would cause
trouble like today.

597
00:43:52,229 --> 00:43:53,163
Ken.

598
00:43:54,965 --> 00:43:56,500
I am not…

599
00:43:58,469 --> 00:43:59,703
human.

600
00:45:51,081 --> 00:45:53,984
I will tell the truth to everyone.

601
00:45:54,051 --> 00:45:56,353
<i>We've got so many phone call</i>
<i>complaints to the radio station.</i>

602
00:45:56,420 --> 00:45:57,654
Let's run away from here.

603
00:45:58,589 --> 00:46:01,959
I will always be with you.

604
00:46:02,025 --> 00:46:04,394
<i>Ken, promise me you will be back.</i>

605
00:46:04,461 --> 00:46:05,496
THIS DRAMA IS FICTION

